## Status Colors Reference

```elixir
:online    -> "bg-[#3ba55c]"  # Green
:away      -> "bg-[#faa61a]"  # Yellow/Orange
:dnd       -> "bg-[#f04747]"  # Red (Do Not Disturb)
:invisible -> "bg-[#747f8d]"  # Gray (appears offline)
:offline   -> "bg-[#747f8d]"  # Gray
```

